ctions in the City’s spiritual realms.%0a---%0a> •••• Medium ••• -Or- Spirit Speech •• and Area of Expertise (Occult: Spirits) • - Spirits are not the only beings that guide the living. Sometimes the dead refuse to sleep and even their voices carry wisdom. As Priests continue to advance in their understanding they learn to listen to these voices as well.%0a> %0a> ••••• Vampires and Ghouls gain the first dot of and access to Blood Tenebrous as a Clan Discipline/Others instead gain Allies (Spirits) 3 - The Bishops of the Invisible Hand know and see the truth. The cult exists as much as an extension of the City Father’s will as it does in an effort to extend influence over Him in order to further their own goals and machinations. Kindred, and their ghoul servants if ever allowed to reach this level of enlightenment, gain the first level of Blood Tenebrous as their blood manifests mysterious gifts in response to the City Father’s presence. Others at this rank simply benefit from increased influence and connections in the City’s spiritual realms.%0a
