diff:1529372799:1529372351:=410,412c410,412%0a%3c || •• || Guardian || '''Moon:'''  1 dot hedgespun weapon, '''Stars:'''  1 dot hedgespun weapon, '''Sky:'''  1 dot hedgespun armor, '''Earth:'''  Esoteric Armory ||%0a%3c || ••• || Knight || '''Moon:'''  Protective:  Temple Guardian (••), '''Stars:'''  Offensive:  Hedge Battler (••), '''Sky:'''  Healing:  Bounty (••), '''Earth:'''  +1 to Crafts ||%0a%3c || •••• || Warden || '''Moon:'''  Augmented Resilience.  Gain 2 dots in stamina which can go above the characters normal cap.  When deprived of willpower she gains 2/1 armor.  '''Stars:'''  Gain three dots in a supernatural or mundane fighting style of your choosing.  If an element is required, theme it towards light or darkness.(•••), '''Sky:'''  Laying on Hands (•••), '''Earth:'''  Master Shaper (•••) ||%0a---%0a> || •• || Guardian || Moon:  1 dot hedgespun weapon, Stars:  1 dot hedgespun weapon, Sky:  1 dot hedgespun armor, Earth:  Esoteric Armory ||%0a> || ••• || Knight || A skill dot or two dot merit: Moon:  Protective:  Temple Guardian (••), Stars:  Offensive:  Hedge Battler (••), Sky:  Healing:  Bounty (••), Earth:  Support:  +1 to Crafts ||%0a> || •••• || Warden || Three dot merit: Moon:  Augmented Resilience.  Gain 2 dots in stamina which can go above the characters normal cap.  When deprived of willpower she gains 2/1 armor.  Stars:  Gain three dots in a supernatural or mundane fighting style of your choosing.  If an element is required, theme it towards light or darkness.(•••), Sky:  Laying on Hands (•••), Earth:  Master Shaper (•••) ||%0a
