diff:1528668234:1527901431:=2,7c2,5%0a%3c ----%0a%3c !%25center%25'''Wanton Wicked's'''%0a%3c !%25center%25'''Mystery Cult'''%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a---%0a> !!!City: Mystery Cult%0a> %0a> %0a> %0a9,11c7,9%0a%3c !!%25center%25'''The Co-Op'''%0a%3c %25center%25(''Supernatural Only - Full Template Required'')%0a%3c %0a---%0a> !!The Co-Op%0a> (Supernatural Only - Full Template Required)%0a> %0a18c16%0a%3c !!!%25center%25''Purpose''%0a---%0a> Purpose%0a21c19%0a%3c !!!%25center%25''Relic''%0a---%0a> Relic%0a24,42c22,38%0a%3c !!!%25center%25''Doctrine''%0a%3c %25center%25''“Now this is the Code of The Co-Op, which every member must know,'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''And the one who keeps it will prosper, but the one who breaks it shall go.'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''As the Willamette flows through Portland, the code goes on without stop;'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''The success of the Co-Op’s the members; the member’s success the Co-Op.'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''Give aid to your fellow members, for they will aid you in return'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''Through cooperative effort and help from each other, each member can thrive and can learn.'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''The room of the member is the member’s, and none this sanctum shall breach;'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''The whole of the building is the Co-Op’s, however, owned and protected by each.'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''Do not inform on your neighbors, nor to mortals their secrets reveal;'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''Visitors of factions are welcome, if they don’t cause hostile zeal.'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''Withhold not your knowledge nor power, from those who share this our abode,'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25center%25''For to do what you can to strengthen each other is the goal of the Code.”'' [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c !!!%25center%25''Mechanics''%0a%3c :%25center%25The Co-Op is open to membership from full supernatural template characters only:%0a%3c :%25center%25(so currently Changelings, Werewolves, Mages, and Vampires):%0a%3c %0a---%0a> Doctrine%0a> The Code of The Co-Op%0a> “Now this is the Code of The Co-Op, which every member must know,%0a> And the one who keeps it will prosper, but the one who breaks it shall go.%0a> As the Willamette flows through Portland, the code goes on without stop;%0a> The success of the Co-Op’s the members; the member’s success the Co-Op.%0a> Give aid to your fellow members, for they will aid you in return%0a> Through cooperative effort and help from each other, each member can thrive and can learn.%0a> The room of the member is the member’s, and none this sanctum shall breach;%0a> The whole of the building is the Co-Op’s, however, owned and protected by each.%0a> Do not inform on your neighbors, nor to mortals their secrets reveal;%0a> Visitors of factions are welcome, if they don’t cause hostile zeal.%0a> Withhold not your knowledge nor power, from those who share this our abode,%0a> For to do what you can to strengthen each other is the goal of the Code.”%0a> Mechanics%0a> The Co-Op is open to membership from full supernatural template characters only (so currently Changelings, Werewolves, Mages, and Vampires):%0a> %0a44d39%0a%3c %0a46d40%0a%3c %0a48d41%0a%3c %0a50d42%0a%3c %0a53,65c45,55%0a%3c :%25center%25Contact: Drake Roberts%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#top|&#8593; back to top]]%0a%3c %0a%3c !!%25center%25'''Heralds of the Void'''%0a%3c %25center%25(''Open Membership'')%0a%3c %0a%3c %25center%25''“You’re special, you know. So few are brought to the central chamber. So few get to touch the Black Stone. So few are truly worthy of The Void’s wisdom. At least, receiving it so directly. But they’ve been watching you. They told me you’re ready. Ready to see just what you’ve been working towards. The transcendence you’re so close to achieving."''%0a%3c %0a%3c %25center%25''"Just this way. Through the hall, and into the door on the left. It’s locked, but it will open for you. Nobody else should be in there. It will be on the altar. You’ll know it. A simple touch, and you’ll hear it. Trust me when I say it will change you forever."''%0a%3c %0a%3c %25center%25''"Me? No, I’m not coming with you. It’s something you have to do alone. But don’t fret. You wouldn’t be doing this if They didn’t already know you were ready for it….”''%0a%3c %0a---%0a> Contact%0a> Drake Roberts%0a> [&#8593; back to top]%0a> %0a> !!Heralds of the Void%0a> (Open Membership)%0a> %0a> “You’re special, you know. So few are brought to the central chamber. So few get to touch the Black Stone. So few are truly worthy of The Void’s wisdom. At least, receiving it so directly. But they’ve been watching you. They told me you’re ready. Ready to see just what you’ve been working towards. The transcendence you’re so close to achieving.%0a> Just this way. Through the hall, and into the door on the left. It’s locked, but it will open for you. Nobody else should be in there. It will be on the altar. You’ll know it. A simple touch, and you’ll hear it. Trust me when I say it will change you forever.%0a> Me? No, I’m not coming with you. It’s something you have to do alone. But don’t fret. You wouldn’t be doing this if They didn’t already know you were ready for it….”%0a> %0a70c60%0a%3c !!!%25center%25''Purpose''%0a---%0a> Purpose%0a73c63%0a%3c !!!%25center%25''Doctrine''%0a---%0a> Doctrine%0a82c72%0a%3c !!!%25center%25''Ties to the setting''%0a---%0a> Ties to the setting%0a85,87c75,77%0a%3c !!!%25center%25''Mechanics''%0a%3c :%25center%25Availability: Kindred involved in the cult (ideally most), most ghouls, and all mortals/supernaturals will use the Mystery Cult Initiation merit, with mechanics as shown below:%0a%3c %0a---%0a> Mechanics%0a> Availability: Kindred involved in the cult (ideally most), most ghouls, and all mortals/supernaturals will use the Mystery Cult Initiation merit, with mechanics as shown below:%0a> %0a98,101c88,90%0a%3c :NOTE: This is not to say a mortal can’t reach this peak. It just means that they won’t be mortal for long.%0a%3c %0a%3c :%25center%25Contact: Falco1029%0a%3c %0a---%0a> NOTE: This is not to say a mortal can’t reach this peak. It just means that they won’t be mortal for long.%0a> Contact%0a> Falco1029%0a
